<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">The insights above are sourced from <b>Nasdaq eVestment Market Lens</b> which tracks institutional allocators’ meetings and mandates, providing ample lead time for managers to get in front of upcoming allocations and manager searches. The platform also provides details on allocators’ and consultants’ manager recommendations, a valuable source of intelligence on competitors’ fees, performance, and even access to their pitchbooks.</span></span></p>

